data.description: You don't want to miss out on this gem. This beautiful home has been recently upgraded and has a magnificent backyard with endless possibilities. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, an open kitchen with granite countertops, new kitchen cabinets and all appliances are stainless steel. The kitchen overlooks the backyard garden. The oversized 2 car garage offers plenty of cabinets for your tools and the perfect space for storage. French doors open to a spacious lanai completely screened with windows. The house has new vinyl flooring throughout, freshly painted inside and outside. And to complete the fantastic look of the house it has LED lights and modern warmth lights too. The roof is 14 years old, the HVAC is two years old. The house is located in the great subdivision Bear Creek, near to popular local attractions, convenient local schools, shopping, restaurants, major roads and parks. This home is MOVE IN READY! Come see it before it is gone!
